title: Songs That Define Us…Amy is About Wanting A Baby + The Guys Rank Their Looks On A Scale of 1-10 +  + Caller Has A Major In-Law Problem
itunes:title: Songs That Define Us…Amy is About Wanting A Baby + The Guys Rank Their Looks On A Scale of 1-10 +  + Caller Has A Major In-Law Problem
description:
Maren Morris shared a new song that she says is her most personal song yet. So we each shares songs that most define our lives. Bobby has the guys rank their own looks as if they were put on truth serum. A listener calls in with his story of a major issue he’s having with his in-law calling him mean names. He wants to know how to deal with it…Eddie shares a similar experience he has with his wife.
